<row>
<entry valign="top" align="left">4. Design and implement educational program</entry>
<entry valign="top" align="left"><list list-type="bulleted" id="list-00006"><item>Finalize curriculum, materials, and resources</item>
<item>Deliver as planned</item>
</list>
</entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry valign="top" align="left">5. Evaluate the educational process and effects of the program</entry>
